          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeUFspP9LOpmnYmDPZKoOMpJGkOkm37HY-LLSHcjAdvjUGSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I cannot say enough great things about Tribeca Dental Care. From the moment you walk in, the experience is professional, welcoming, and calming.\n\nDr. Tang is truly exceptional. I used to hate going to the dentist and felt a lot of fear and anxiety, but Dr. Tang completely changed that for me. He takes the time to explain everything clearly, answers all questions, and most importantly provides painless, high-quality care. I felt safe, heard, and extremely well taken care of.\n\nDavid, the hygienist/assistant, is fantastic, very gentle, knowledgeable, and reassuring throughout the entire visit. He made the experience smooth and comfortable.\n\nA big thank you as well to Diane at the front desk. She is professional, kind, and incredibly helpful, making scheduling and check-in stress-free.\nBecause of this team, I actually look forward to going to the dentist now, something I never thought I\u2019d say. Highly recommend Tribeca Dental Care to anyone looking for excellent dental care with a compassionate and skilled team.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSTmNubHBlblpSVTFaNlVWbE5iRXQyTTNkcVVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x940aaf0b82a61d1a!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkRNcnlpenZRU1Z6UVlNbEt2M3dqUUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
