          "description": "This place is awesome. Their Invisalign price is very good compared to what other Manhattan dentists quoted me (literally 3 times less than one place). They have dependable service and a flexible schedule.\n\nWhen I finished up my Invisalign treatment, they also replaced 2 very visible fillings in my front teeth. They look SO MUCH better now. I\u2019ve had fillings in those teeth for years and I have never liked how they looked until now.\n\nAll this to say, if you want to do a \u2018smile renovation,\u2019 definitely choose a cosmetic dentist like this place.",
